CustomerDuplicateValueException

if a {@code Customer} {@code Entity}
	 *                                         with the same {@code email} already
	 *                                         exists.
	 
	 
CustomerNullValueException

if the {@code Customer}
	 *                                         {@code Entity} has any {@code null}
	 *                                         values in it.
	 
CustomerIsNullException

if the <code>Customer</code> value is
	 *                                         {@code null}
	 
	 
	 
CompanyNullValueException

if the {@code Company} {@code Entity}
	 *                                        has any {@code null} values in it.
	 
CompanyDuplicateValueException 

if a {@code Company} {@code Entity}
	 *                                        with the same {@code name} or
	 *                                        {@code email} already exists.
	 
CompanyIsNullException 

if the {@code Company} {@code Entity}
	 *                                        is {@code null}
	 